(1, 1, 'BGIS - One of the Top Boarding', '1394713253.jpg', '<style type=\"text/css\">\n.donate_main_links {\n	font-family:Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;\n	float:left;\n	width:76%;\nmargin-left: 8px;\n}\n.donate_in {\n	float:left;\n	border:1px solid #ccc;\n	-webkit-border-radius: 5px;\n	-moz-border-radius: 5px;\n	border-radius: 5px;\n}\n.donate_in ul {\n	float: left;\n	margin:0px;\n	padding:0px;\n}\n.donate_in ul li img {\n	float: left;\n	margin: 0px;\n	padding: 0px;\n	margin-right: 10px;\n}\n.donate_in ul li {\n	float:left;\n	margin:0px;\n	padding:20px;\n	list-style:none;\n}\n.tooltip {\n	display:none;\n	width:300px;\n	line-height:160%;\n	margin-left:-70px;\n	position:absolute;\n	border:1px solid #ccc;\n	background-color:#f8f8f8;\n	border-radius:5px;\n	padding:10px;\n	color:#000;\n	font-size:16px;\n	font-family:calibri;\n}\n</style>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\n$(document).ready(function() {\n        // Tooltip only Text\n        $(\'.masterTooltip\').hover(function(){\n                // Hover over code\n                var title = $(this).attr(\'title\');\n                $(this).data(\'tipText\', title).removeAttr(\'title\');\n                $(\'<p class=\"tooltip\"></p>\')\n                .text(title)\n                .appendTo(\'body\')\n                .fadeIn(\'slow\');\n        }, function() {\n                // Hover out code\n                $(this).attr(\'title\', $(this).data(\'tipText\'));\n                $(\'.tooltip\').remove();\n        }).mousemove(function(e) {\n                var mousex = e.pageX + 20; //Get X coordinates\n                var mousey = e.pageY + 10; //Get Y coordinates\n                $(\'.tooltip\')\n                .css({ top: mousey, left: mousex })\n        });\n});\n</script>      \n   <div class=\"aboutus\">\n          <h2>Meet the Founder </h2>\n          <p> <img src=\"../img/founderimg.jpg\" style=\"float:right; padding:5px; padding-left:10px;\" />The Bhaktivedanta Gurukula and International School was founded by renowned scholar and devotee A.C. Bhaktivedanta Swami Prabhupada, founder-acharya of the International Society for Krishna Consciousness (ISKCON). Srila Prabhupada single-handedly spread Vaisnava/Hindu dharma all over the world, establishing 108 temples and several schools in India and throughout the West.\nSrila Prabhupada, a highly educated leader, exemplifies the kind of education that BGIS offers and the kind of graduate that BGIS hopes to produce. He was kind, bold, influential, humble, humourous, gentle, balanced, hard-working, respectful, highly spiritual, determined and an excellent communicator - both as a speaker and as a writer.\nHe felt equally at home in an Indian village and in a busy Western metropolis. He could converse meaningfully with a simple worker and a head of state. Business, math, the gentle art of persuasion, philosophy and four languages - he was proficient in it all. He cared deeply for people and touched the hearts of all he met.\nWe at BGIS are awed by his abilities and character, and we hope that this, his school, continues to represent his qualities and pass them on. Which is what we strive towards through our teachers and students.\n\nKnow more about Srila Prabhupada</p>\n          <h2>Mission Statement :</h2>\n          <p>â€œTo prepare fine citizens of the world, men of character and competence, who can lead and inspire others.â€</p>\n          <!--h2>Goals :</h2>\n          <p>To train and educate for personal success in the following:<br />\n â€¢               the art and science of loving and serving Krishna (Bhakti Yoga)<br />\nâ€¢               academic and co-curricular requirements for future study and work character development and life skills</p-->\n        </div>\n<div class=\"down\">&nbsp;</div>\n<h2 style=\"position: relative;font-size: 15px;color: #a0030b;margin: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 10px;\">Donate For Complete Education</h2>\n<div class=\"down\">&nbsp;</div>\n  <div class=\"donate_main_links\">\n  <div class=\"donate_in\">\n   <ul>\n      <li><a href=\"/contributes/online-payment\"><img src=\"../img/campus.png\" class=\"masterTooltip\" title=\"New BGIS  Development\" /></a> </li>\n      <li><a href=\"/onlinepayments/c92b26f68689c7af56b0b08721897732\"><img src=\"../img/cow.png\" class=\"masterTooltip\" title=\"Cow Care : Help us maintain the cows for a year.\" /></a> </li>\n      <li><a href=\"/onlinepayments/2cad8fa47bbef282badbb8de5374b894\"><img src=\"../img/invest.png\" class=\"masterTooltip\" title=\"Invest for your future\" /></a> </li>\n      <li><a href=\"/onlinepayments/b7a782741f667201b54880c925faec4b\"><img src=\"../img/nature.png\" class=\"masterTooltip\" title=\"Nature Care  : Support 15 trees for life.\" /></a> </li>\n      <li><a href=\"/onlinepayments/14ee22eaba297944c96afdbe5b16c65b\"><img src=\"../img/sponser.png\" class=\"masterTooltip\" title=\"Child Education, Sponsor the Education of One Child for a year  including residential charges .\" /></a> </li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n</div>', '2014-03-13', 1),
(2, 2, 'BGIS - One of the Top Boarding', '1394714125.jpg', '<style type=\"text/css\">\r\n.donate_main_links {\r\n	font-family:Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;\r\n	float:left;\r\n	width:76%;\r\nmargin-left: 8px;\r\n}\r\n.donate_in {\r\n	float:left;\r\n	border:1px solid #ccc;\r\n	-webkit-border-radius: 5px;\r\n	-moz-border-radius: 5px;\r\n	border-radius: 5px;\r\n}\r\n.donate_in ul {\r\n	float: left;\r\n	margin:0px;\r\n	padding:0px;\r\n}\r\n.donate_in ul li img {\r\n	float: left;\r\n	margin: 0px;\r\n	padding: 0px;\r\n	margin-right: 10px;\r\n}\r\n.donate_in ul li {\r\n	float:left;\r\n	margin:0px;\r\n	padding:20px;\r\n	list-style:none;\r\n}\r\n.tooltip {\r\n	display:none;\r\n	width:300px;\r\n	line-height:160%;\r\n	margin-left:-70px;\r\n	position:absolute;\r\n	border:1px solid #ccc;\r\n	background-color:#f8f8f8;\r\n	border-radius:5px;\r\n	padding:10px;\r\n	color:#000;\r\n	font-size:16px;\r\n	font-family:calibri;\r\n}\r\n</style>\r\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\r\n$(document).ready(function() {\r\n        // Tooltip only Text\r\n        $(\'.masterTooltip\').hover(function(){\r\n                // Hover over code\r\n                var title = $(this).attr(\'title\');\r\n                $(this).data(\'tipText\', title).removeAttr(\'title\');\r\n                $(\'<p class=\"tooltip\"></p>\')\r\n                .text(title)\r\n                .appendTo(\'body\')\r\n                .fadeIn(\'slow\');\r\n        }, function() {\r\n                // Hover out code\r\n                $(this).attr(\'title\', $(this).data(\'tipText\'));\r\n                $(\'.tooltip\').remove();\r\n        }).mousemove(function(e) {\r\n                var mousex = e.pageX + 20; //Get X coordinates\r\n                var mousey = e.pageY + 10; //Get Y coordinates\r\n                $(\'.tooltip\')\r\n                .css({ top: mousey, left: mousex })\r\n        });\r\n});\r\n</script>  \r\n\r\n <div class=\"aboutus\">\r\n          <h2>â€œA sound mind in a sound body, is a short, but full description of a happy state in this worldâ€</h2>\r\n          <p> <img src=\"../img/whatmakesus.jpg\" style=\"padding:5px; float:right; padding-left:10px;\" />BGIS has a unique approach for over all development of your child. When we say â€˜over-allâ€™ it not only includes  high class education and excellent sports facilities, but practice of its  true meaning which emphasizes  on sharp, healthy and sound mind as well. \r\n            A stable sound mind is possible through meditation practices, and value-based education. It helps in absorbing the best and able to battle against stress and pressure in this competitive world.  Here, your child will also get moral teachings which will help him to become a responsible son and a responsible citizen for his nation.\r\n              This is a school with a difference wherein your child will receive wholesome education which fills the void which the modern education is unable to fill alone.</p>\r\n             <h2>BGIS believes in holistic development of your child, which incorporates:</h2>\r\n          <p>1 High quality education system with IIT graduates in our faculty<br />\r\n                2  Sports facilities -Soccer fields, Volleyball, badminton, handball, and basketball courts, swimming pool, table tennis.<br />\r\n                3 Co-curricular activities in addition to Mridanga classes from world famous mridanga player, Bablu Das Mahasaya.<br />\r\n                4 Value-based education<br />\r\n                5 Teachers and students from many countries all over the world bring an unique international ambience.<br />\r\n                6 Special career guidance and counseling by I.I.T graduates and MBAâ€™s   for the students of +2 standards.<br />\r\n                7 Adventurous and fun-filled spiritual retreats help students to develop strong and versatile personalities.<br />\r\n                8 Unique hostel environment with one warden assigned for every 18 students<br />  \r\n                9 Teacher-student ratio of 1:10 makes learning experience thoroughly absorbing.<br />\r\n               10 Co-curricular activities include astronomy, music, drama, photography, animation</p>\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"down\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"position: relative;font-size: 15px;color: #a0030b;margin: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 10px;\">Donate For Complete Education</h2>\r\n<div class=\"down\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n  <div class=\"donate_main_links\">\r\n  <div class=\"donate_in\">\r\n    <ul>\r\n      <li><a href=\"/contributes/online-payment\"><img src=\"../img/campus.png\" class=\"masterTooltip\" title=\"New BGIS  Development\" /></a> </li>\r\n      <li><a href=\"/onlinepayments/c92b26f68689c7af56b0b08721897732\"><img src=\"../img/cow.png\" class=\"masterTooltip\" title=\"Cow Care : Help us maintain the cows for a year.\" /></a> </li>\r\n      <li><a href=\"/onlinepayments/2cad8fa47bbef282badbb8de5374b894\"><img src=\"../img/invest.png\" class=\"masterTooltip\" title=\"Invest for your future\" /></a> </li>\r\n      <li><a href=\"/onlinepayments/b7a782741f667201b54880c925faec4b\"><img src=\"../img/nature.png\" class=\"masterTooltip\" title=\"Nature Care  : Support 15 trees for life.\" /></a> </li>\r\n      <li><a href=\"/onlinepayments/14ee22eaba297944c96afdbe5b16c65b\"><img src=\"../img/sponser.png\" class=\"masterTooltip\" title=\"Child Education, Sponsor the Education of One Child for a year  including residential charges .\" /></a> </li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>', '2014-03-13', 1),
(3, 3, 'BGIS - One of the Top Boarding', '1394714331.jpg', '<style type=\"text/css\">\r\n.donate_main_links {\r\n	font-family:Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;\r\n	float:left;\r\n	width:76%;\r\nmargin-left: 8px;\r\n}\r\n.donate_in {\r\n	float:left;\r\n	border:1px solid #ccc;\r\n	-webkit-border-radius: 5px;\r\n	-moz-border-radius: 5px;\r\n	border-radius: 5px;\r\n}\r\n.donate_in ul {\r\n	float: left;\r\n	margin:0px;\r\n	padding:0px;\r\n}\r\n.donate_in ul li img {\r\n	float: left;\r\n	margin: 0px;\r\n	padding: 0px;\r\n	margin-right: 10px;\r\n}\r\n.donate_in ul li {\r\n	float:left;\r\n	margin:0px;\r\n	padding:20px;\r\n	list-style:none;\r\n}\r\n.tooltip {\r\n	display:none;\r\n	width:300px;\r\n	line-height:160%;\r\n	margin-left:-70px;\r\n	position:absolute;\r\n	border:1px solid #ccc;\r\n	background-color:#f8f8f8;\r\n	border-radius:5px;\r\n	padding:10px;\r\n	color:#000;\r\n	font-size:16px;\r\n	font-family:calibri;\r\n}\r\n.campuspage{}\r\n.cf_1{ float:left; width:745px;}\r\n.cf_1 h1{ margin:10px; font-family:calibri; font-size:24px; color:#a0030b;}\r\n.cf_1 p{ margin:10px; padding:0px; font-family:calibri; font-size:14px; color:#6a6a6a;}\r\nimg.floatLeft { \r\n    float: left; \r\n    margin: 4px; \r\n}\r\nimg.floatRight { \r\n    float: right; \r\n    margin: 4px; \r\n}\r\nimg.floatRightClear { \r\n    float: right; \r\n    clear: right; \r\n    margin: 4px; \r\n}\r\n</style>\r\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\r\n$(document).ready(function() {\r\n        // Tooltip only Text\r\n        $(\'.masterTooltip\').hover(function(){\r\n                // Hover over code\r\n                var title = $(this).attr(\'title\');\r\n                $(this).data(\'tipText\', title).removeAttr(\'title\');\r\n                $(\'<p class=\"tooltip\"></p>\')\r\n                .text(title)\r\n                .appendTo(\'body\')\r\n                .fadeIn(\'slow\');\r\n        }, function() {\r\n                // Hover out code\r\n                $(this).attr(\'title\', $(this).data(\'tipText\'));\r\n                $(\'.tooltip\').remove();\r\n        }).mousemove(function(e) {\r\n                var mousex = e.pageX + 20; //Get X coordinates\r\n                var mousey = e.pageY + 10; //Get Y coordinates\r\n                $(\'.tooltip\')\r\n                .css({ top: mousey, left: mousex })\r\n        });\r\n});\r\n</script> \r\n<div class=\"campuspage\">\r\n  <div class=\"cf_1\">\r\n    <img src=\"../img/campusfacilities1.jpg\" class=\"floatLeft\">\r\n    <p>Bhaktivedanta Gurukula and International School (BGIS) is located in Raman Reti, Vrindavan which is the abode of Lord Krishna and home to over 5,000 temples. The campus is situated next to Sri Sri Krishna Balram Temple (ISKCON) which is a national heritage. The campus of BGIS incorporates both the residential and academic facilities, was built in 1977.</p>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"cf_1\">\r\n    <h1>Campus is equipped with:</h1>\r\n    <img src=\"../img/campusfacilities2.jpg\" class=\"floatLeft\" style=\"margin-right: 25px;\">\r\n    <p>\r\n    <ul style=\"margin-left: 25px;font-size: 15px;color: #6a6a6a;\"> \r\n      <li>Spacious academic classrooms</li><br />\r\n      <li> Library with audio-visual lab</li><br />\r\n      <li>Science lab</li><br />\r\n      <li> Computer lab</li><br />\r\n      <li>Football, Volleyball and handball ground</li><br />\r\n      <li>Swimming pool and basketball court</li><br />\r\n      <li>Badminton and Table tennis facilities</li><br />\r\n      <li> Uninterrupted power supply</li><br />\r\n      <li>24Ã—7 Security Services</li><br />\r\n      <li>24Ã—7 medical care with daily doctor visit.</li><br />\r\n      <li>Reverse Osmosis water purification plant, supplying water for drinking and cooking.</li><br />\r\n      <li>.Residential ashrams with bunk beds, 2 to 6 students per room along with personal study desks and bathrooms with double-spout tap (one for hot and one for cold water).\r\n</li><br/></ul> </p>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"cf_1\">\r\n    \r\n    <table>\r\n      <tr>\r\n        <td style=\"padding:10px;\"><img src=\"../img/cp01.png\" /></td>\r\n        <td style=\"padding:10px;\"><img src=\"../img/cp02.png\" /></td>\r\n        <td style=\"padding:10px;\"><img src=\"../img/cp03.png\" /></td>\r\n        <td style=\"padding:10px;\"><img src=\"../img/cp04.png\" /></td>\r\n      </tr>\r\n    </table>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"cf_1\">\r\n    <p>We are glad to inform you about the construction of our new campus on 100 acres of land. Please take a closer  look </p>\r\n   <br/>\r\n<span><a href=\"http://newbgis.org/\"  target=\"_blank\"  style=\"color:#a0030b;position: relative;font-size: 15px; margin-left: 10px;top: -10px;\">Click Here to know more</a></span>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"down\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"position: relative;font-size: 15px;color: #a0030b;margin: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 10px;\">Donate For Complete Education</h2>\r\n<div class=\"down\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n  <div class=\"donate_main_links\">\r\n  <div class=\"donate_in\">\r\n    <ul>\r\n      <li><a href=\"/contributes/online-payment\"><img src=\"../img/campus.png\" class=\"masterTooltip\" title=\"New BGIS  Development\" /></a> </li>\r\n      <li><a href=\"/onlinepayments/c92b26f68689c7af56b0b08721897732\"><img src=\"../img/cow.png\" class=\"masterTooltip\" title=\"Cow Care : Help us maintain the cows for a year.\" /></a> </li>\r\n      <li><a href=\"/onlinepayments/2cad8fa47bbef282badbb8de5374b894\"><img src=\"../img/invest.png\" class=\"masterTooltip\" title=\"Invest for your future\" /></a> </li>\r\n      <li><a href=\"/onlinepayments/b7a782741f667201b54880c925faec4b\"><img src=\"../img/nature.png\" class=\"masterTooltip\" title=\"Nature Care  : Support 15 trees for life.\" /></a> </li>\r\n      <li><a href=\"/onlinepayments/14ee22eaba297944c96afdbe5b16c65b\"><img src=\"../img/sponser.png\" class=\"masterTooltip\" title=\"Child Education, Sponsor the Education of One Child for a year  including residential charges .\" /></a> </li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>', '2014-03-13', 1);
INSERT INTO `admission` (`id`, `menu_id`, `page_title`, `banner_image`, `content`, `created`, `status`) VALUES
(1, 8, 'BGIS - One of the Top Boarding', '1394715886.jpg', '<div class=\"aboutus\">\n  <p style=\"width: 700px;margin-left: 42px;font-size: 17px !important;font-family: calibri;color: #7e7e7e;\n  line-height: 130%;\"> <img src=\"../img/howtoapplyinner.jpg\" style=\"padding:5px; padding-left:15px; float:right;\" />\n    \n    <img src=\"../img/iconhowtoapply.png\" / style=\"  position: absolute;margin-left: -44px;\">\n    Thank you for showing interest in Bhaktivedanta Gurukula and International School (BGIS).<br />\n    <br/>\n  BGIS is a school with a difference. Our emphasis is on creating character in each child who joins us.  The character will be formed if given proper training from the very child hood.  However whenever a child joins BGIS at any age, we inculcate in the child the fundamental spiritual, moral & social values which can mould a child to become children with perfect character & competence who can lead and inspire others.<br />\n    <br/>\n   The candidate has to appear for an admission test which will determine the child\'s aptitude in English, Mathematics and Science. This will be followed by an interview with both the child and  the parents.</p>\n  <br/>\n<h2 style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">Please call Admission Office to fix your Admission Date.</h2>\n        <h3 style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">Admissions open for classes 2-9 only</h3>\n        <h3 style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">Next Admission Dates Will Update Soon</h3> \n  <br/>\n  <img src=\"../img/iconvenue.png\" / style=\"  position: absolute;margin-left: -3px;\">\n  <h2 style=\"font-size: 20px !important;\n  font-family: calibri;\n  color: #000; margin-left: 42px;\">Venue</h2>\n  <p style=\"\n  margin-left: 42px;\n  font-size: 17px !important;\n  font-family: calibri;\n  color: #7e7e7e;\n  line-height: 142%;\">Bhaktivedanta Gurukula and International School<br />\n    Bhaktivedanta Swami Marg,<br />\n    Raman Reti, Vrindavan, Mathura<br />\n    Uttar Pradesh, 281121</p>\n    \n  <img src=\"../img/iocntime.png\" / style=\"  position: absolute;margin-left: -3px;\">\n  <h2 style=\"font-size: 20px !important;\n  font-family: calibri;\n  color: #000; margin-left: 42px;\">Timing</h2>\n  <p style=\"\n  margin-left: 42px;\n  font-size: 17px !important;\n  font-family: calibri;\n  color: #7e7e7e;\n  line-height: 142%;\">Timing: 10.00 AM Sharp<br />\n    Registration fee: 1000/- Rupees</p>\n    \n    <img src=\"../img/iconhowtopay.png\" / style=\"  position: absolute;margin-left: -3px;\">\n  <h2 style=\"font-size: 20px !important;\n  font-family: calibri;\n  color: #000; margin-left: 42px;\">How to Pay:</h2>\n  <p style=\"\n  margin-left: 42px;\n  font-size: 17px !important;\n  font-family: calibri;\n  color: #7e7e7e;\n  line-height: 142%;\">You can enrol for admission test directly at school reception office.  Please bring \"Demand Draft\" (DD) in favor of â€˜Bhaktivedanta Gurukula and International Schoolâ€™, payable at Axis bank Vrindavan (code: 0794) .  Please note cash will not be accepted in school. You may also register by post / online.  You may post the DD or proof of NEFT / online transfer to the school address along with the registration form</p>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size: 20px !important;\n  font-family: calibri;\n  color: #000; margin-left: 42px;\">Internet banking :</h2>\n  <p style=\"\n  margin-left: 42px;\n  font-size: 17px !important;\n  font-family: calibri;\n  color: #7e7e7e;\n  line-height: 142%;\">\nSchool : Bhaktivedanta Gurukula and International School \n<br/>Bank : Axis bank, Vrindavan\n<br/>\nAccount number :  910010021205638\n<br/>\nIFSC code: UTIB0000794\n<br/>\nSwift code: AXISIN B002\n<br/>\n After bank transfer please send the registration form along with transaction details or bank slip to our postal address.\n<br/>\nBhaktivedanta Gurukula and International School (ISKCON)\n<br/>\nBhaktivedanta Swami Marg,<br/>\nRaman Reti, Vrindavan, Mathura<br/>\nUttar Pradesh, 281121</p>\n  <p style=\"\n  margin-left: 42px;\n  font-size: 20px !important;\n  font-family: calibri;\n  color: #000; font-weight:bold;\"> Kindly fill the e-form below and send for registration for admission test or you may take a print out and send it by post or give in person at our admission office in Vrindavan.</b>\n  <!--h2><a href=\"http://bgis.org/onlineregister\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"margin-left: 42px;\"><img src=\"../img/click-here-for-e-form.png\"></a></h2-->\n  </p>\n  \n  \n  <img src=\"../img/iconphone.png\" / style=\"  position: absolute;margin-left: -3px;\">\n  <h2 style=\"\n  margin-left: 42px;\n  font-size: 18px !important;\n  font-family: calibri;\n  color: #000;\">For more information please contact:-</h2>\n  <br />\n  <span style=\"\n  margin-left: 42px;color: #9D0000;\"><b>+91 - 7088004339 , +91 - 7088004342 </b></span>\n  <h2 style=\"\n  margin-left: 42px;\n  font-size: 18px !important;\n  font-family: calibri;\n  color: #000;\">NOTE:</h2>\n  <p style=\"\n  margin-left: 42px;\n  font-size: 16px !important;\n  font-family: calibri;\n  color: #000; font-weight:bold;\">1. We have limited seats and all admissions will be considered on a First come First served basis.<br />\n    2. The enrollment fees will be non refundable.</p>\n</div>', '2014-03-13', 1),
