">\r\n              <h2>Expanding the education that stays for life.</h2>\r\n              <p style=\" font-style:italic;\">The current strength of the school has exceeded the present buildingâ€™s capacity of 250 students. Srila Prabhupada had the desire that more than 500 students study in the Vrindavana Gurukula.( SP Lilamrita Chapter 52). To fulfill Srila Prabhupadâ€™s desire and to provide world-class Education Model. BGIS needs EXPANSION. \r\n                The BGIS modal of education is based on Indian Gurukula style of education adapted to contempoary societal needs. A world-class infrastructure will be developed for more than 600 school students and 400 college students knowledge generation initiatives will be taken across disciplines such as science, mathematics, Classical Music, Performing art, Fine arts, Learning methodologies \r\n                and sanskrit studies</p>\r\n              <div class=\"landinfra\">\r\n                <div class=\"landmark\">\r\n                  <h1>Land & Location</h1>\r\n                  <h2>In the Holy Land, at the Perfect Location.</h2>\r\n                  <p><img src=\"../img/mapbgis.jpg\" /></p>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"infrastructure\">\r\n                  <h1>Infrastructure Highlights</h1>\r\n                  <h2>The perfection of best products, design & functionality</h2>\r\n                  <p><img src=\"../img/infrabgis.jpg\" /></p>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"siteplan\">\r\n                  <h1>Site Plan</h1>\r\n                  <div class=\"imagezoom\">\r\n                    <p> <a class=\"fancybox\" href=\"../demo1/1_b.jpg\" style=\"padding:10px;\" data-fancybox-group=\"gallery\" ><img src=\"../demo1/1_s.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a> <a class=\"fancybox\" href=\"../demo1/2_b.jpg\" style=\"padding:10px;\" data-fancybox-group=\"gallery\" ><img src=\"../demo1/2_s.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a> <a class=\"fancybox\" href=\"../demo1/3_b.jpg\" style=\"padding:10px;\" data-fancybox-group=\"gallery\" ><img src=\"../demo1/3_s.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a> <a class=\"fancybox\" style=\"padding:10px;\" href=\"../demo1/4_b.jpg\" data-fancybox-group=\"gallery\" ><img src=\"../demo1/4_s.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a> <a class=\"fancybox\" style=\"padding:10px;\" href=\"../demo1/5_b.jpg\" data-fancybox-group=\"gallery\" ><img src=\"../demo1/5_s.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a> </p>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n              </div>\r\n            </div>', '2014-05-09', 1),
(2, 25, 'Team new bgis campus', '1399619459.jpg', '<div class=\"vision\">\n          <h2><span style=\"color: #94020a;\">The team :</span> We are ready </h2>\n          <div class=\"teampic\">\n            <ul>\n              <li><img src=\"../img/team/t1.png\" />\n                <p>HH Gopal Krishna Maharaj<br />\n                  GBC ISKCON</p>\n              </li>\n              \n              <li><img src=\"../img/team/t3.png\" />\n                <p>Dr. Lila Purushottam Das<br />\n                  Director, BGIS<br />\n                  (Phd, Prof, IIT Kanpur)</p>\n              </li>\n              \n             <li><img src=\"../img/team/t2.png\" />\n                <p>Rakesh Uberoi<br />\n                 CEO - Partnership Innovation<br />\n                  BGIS\n                  </p>\n              </li>\n\n\n              \n              <!--li><img src=\"../img/team/t5.png\" />\n                <p>Nishant Vashisht<br />\n                  Coordinator, Botanical Garden<br />\n                  (Designer, NIFT Delhi)</p>\n              </li-->\n              <li><img src=\"../img/team/t6.png\" />\n                <p>Radhakant Das<br />\n                  Project Manager<br />\n                  (B.Tech, M.Tech, IIT Kanpur)</p>\n              </li>\n              <li><img src=\"../img/team/t7.png\" />\n                <p>Mayank Singh<br />\n                  New Project Coordinator<br />\n                  (B.Tech, MBA, IIT Kanpur)</p>\n              </li>\n            </ul>\n          </div>\n        </div>', '2014-05-09', 1),
(4, 26, 'Road map of bgis', '1399619880.jpg', '<div class=\"roadmap\">\n          <h2>Roadmap<span style=\"color:#393939;\"> of the project </span></h2>\n          <div class=\"down\">&nbsp;</div>\n          <h2>Year 2012-13</h2>\n          <p>60 Acres of Land Acquired </p>\n          <h2>Year 2013-14</h2>\n          <p>Completion of master plan and start of contsruction </p>\n          <h2>Year 2016</h2>\n          <p>Completion of 1st phase construction </p>\n          <h2>Year 2018</h2>\n          <p>Knowledge generation through specialized courses </p>\n          <h2>Year 2019</h2>\n          <p>Working on innovative models of intellectual management for the welfare of the society with spiritual outlook </p>\n          <h2>Year 2020</h2>\n          <p>Full Fledged University </p>\n        </div>', '2014-05-09', 1),
(5, 27, 'Construction cost for new bgis', '1399620537.jpg', '<div class=\"vision\">\n          <h2><span style=\"color:#000000\">1st Phase</span> construction</h2>\n          <div class=\"firstphase\">\n            <ul>\n              <li><img src=\"../img/academicbuilding.jpg\" />\n                <p> <span style=\"font-size:15px;\">Academic building</span><br />\n                  â€¢ Class rooms<br />\n                  â€¢ Library: books<br />\n                  â€¢ School Bus<br />\n                  â€¢ IT Lab </p>\n              </li>\n              <li><img src=\"../img/hostel.jpg\" />\n                <p> <span style=\"font-size:15px;\">Hostel</span><br />\n                  â€¢ Hostel room <br />\n                  â€¢ Kitchen with dining room<br />\n                  â€¢ Swimming pool<br />\n                  <br />\n                </p>\n              </li>\n              <li><img src=\"../img/guest.jpg\" />\n                <p> <span style=\"font-size:15px;\">Guest house </span><br />\n                  â€¢ Guest rooms<br />\n                  â€¢ Library<br />\n                  â€¢ Reception <br />\n                  <br />\n                </p>\n              </li>\n              <li><img src=\"../img/garden.jpg\" />\n                <p> <span style=\"font-size:15px;\">Botanical garden</span><br />\n                  â€¢ Educational park<br />\n                  â€¢ Conservation centre<br />\n                  â€¢ Research centre<br />\n                  <br />\n                </p>\n              </li>\n              <li><img src=\"../img/library.jpg\" />\n                <p> <span style=\"font-size:15px;\">Library</span><br />\n                  â€¢ Books and journal<br />\n                  â€¢ Audio visual System<br />\n                  â€¢ Reading Hall<br />\n                </p>\n              </li>\n              <li><img src=\"../img/centre.jpg\" />\n                <p> <span style=\"font-size:15px;\">Cultural centre with Auditorium</span><br />\n                  â€¢ A beautiful Temple & Prayer hall<br />\n                  â€¢ Auditorium<br />\n                  â€¢ Art & music centre<br />\n                </p>\n              </li>\n            </ul>\n            <div class=\"Participation\">\n              <h1>Your Participation</h1>\n              <h2>Estimated Cost Of Project</h2>\n              <div class=\"data\">\n                <p style=\"float:left;  padding:10px; margin:0px\">Academic Building Complex </p>\n                <p style=\"float:right;padding:10px; margin:0px\">(9570 sq-m) </p>\n              </div>\n        <div class=\"data\">\n                <p style=\"float:left;  padding:10px; margin:0px\">Hostel Complex </p>\n                <p style=\"float:right;padding:10px; margin:0px\">(7500 sq-m) </p>\n              </div>\n               <div class=\"data\">\n                <p style=\"float:left;  padding:10px; margin:0px\">Temple cum auditorium hall   </p>\n                <p style=\"float:right;padding:10px; margin:0px\">(900 sq-m) </p>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"data2\">\n                <p style=\"float:left;  padding:10px; margin:0px\">Total Construction first phase : </p>\n                <p style=\"float:right;padding:10px; margin:0px\">appx.2 lac sq ft </p>\n              </div>\n               <div class=\"data\">\n                <p style=\"float:left;  padding:10px; margin:0px\">Botanical Garden and education park (area 20 acres)                                                \ntotal estimated cost  </p>\n                <p style=\"float:right;padding:10px; margin:0px\"> 4 crores) </p>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"data2\">\n                <p style=\"float:left;  padding:10px; margin:0px\">Estimated total cost of project :   </p>\n                <p style=\"float:right;padding:10px; margin:0px\">34 crores </p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n    <div class=\"down\">&nbsp;</div>\n    <div class=\"somepoints\">\n    <h1>Shri Jagannath Seva: 1 Crore ( Area 5000 sq-ft)</h1>\n    <p>â€¢ Help in construction of temple-cum-auditorium hall of a capacity of 800 students and dedicate it to your dear ones.</p>\n    <h1>Nimai Pandit Seva : 50 lac ( Area 2500 sq-ft)</h1>\n    <p>â€¢ Sponsor the construction of air-conditioned central library and dedicate it to your dear ones.</p>\n    <h1>Aryabhatta Seva : 20 lac ( Area 1100 sq-ft)</h1>\n    <p>â€¢ Under this seva you will help to establish one of the six Science labs in the school.</p>\n    <h1>Sandipani Muni Seva- 11 lac (Area 750 sq-ft)</h1>\n    <p>â€¢ Under this seva you will help in construction of one of the 28 classrooms</p>\n    <h1>Vrindavan Vasi Seva- 8 lac (450 sq-ft)</h1>\n    <p>â€¢ Under this seva you will help in construction of one of the 60 hostel rooms.</p>\n     <h1>Vidya daan seva â€“ 2 lac</h1>\n    <p>â€¢ Sponsor the cost of 500 books for one entire section of library.</p>\n      <h1>Vrindaranyam Seva â€“ 1 lac</h1>\n    <p>â€¢ Sponsor for plantation and maintenance of 150 trees in Vrindaranyam botanical garden.</p>\n    </div>\n        </div>', '2014-05-09', 0),
(6, 24, 'what make us special', '1399623119.jpg', '        <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"../css/slidorion.css\" />\r\n	<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"../js/jquery.tools.min.js\"></script>\r\n	<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"../js/jquery.easing.1.3.js\"></script>\r\n<!-- Add fancyBox main JS and CSS files -->\r\n\r\n	<script type=\"text/javascript\">\r\n	\r\n		$(function() {\r\n			\r\n			var indicator = $(\'#indicator\'),\r\n					indicatorHalfWidth = indicator.width()/2,\r\n					lis = $(\'#tabs\').children(\'li\');\r\n\r\n			$(\"#tabs\").tabs(\"#content section\", {\r\n				effect: \'fade\',\r\n				fadeOutSpeed: 0,\r\n				fadeInSpeed: 400,\r\n				onBeforeClick: function(event, index) {\r\n					var li = lis.eq(index),\r\n					    newPos = li.position().left + (li.width()/2) - indicatorHalfWidth;\r\n					indicator.stop(true).animate({ left: newPos }, 600, \'easeInOutExpo\');\r\n				}\r\n			});	\r\n\r\n		});\r\n\r\n	</script>\r\n	<script src=\"../js/jquery.slidorion.min.js\"></script>\r\n	<script>\r\n	$(document).ready(function(){\r\n		\r\n		$(\'#slidorion\').slidorion();\r\n		\r\n		$(\'.effects\').hide();\r\n		$(\'.more-effects\').click(function(e){\r\n			$(\'.effects\').slideToggle();\r\n			e.preventDefault();\r\n		});\r\n	});\r\n	\r\n	</script>\r\n<script>\r\n                                                $(document).ready(function(e)\r\n                                                          {	\r\n						                             $(\"#one\").click(function ()\r\n					                                 {\r\n										     $(\'#one\').attr(\'src\', \'../images/one_active.jpg\');\r\n                                                                                     $(\'#two\').attr(\'src\', \'../img/two.jpg\');\r\n                                                                                     $(\'#three\').attr(\'src\', \'../img/three.jpg\');\r\n                                                                                     $(\'#four\').attr(\'src\', \'../img/four.jpg\');\r\n                                                                                     $(\'#five\').attr(\'src\', \'../img/five.jpg\');\r\n                                                                        });\r\n                                                                           $(\"#two\").click(function ()\r\n					                                 {\r\n										  $(\'#two\').attr(\'src\', \'../images/two_active.jpg\');\r\n                                                                                    $(\'#one\').attr(\'src\', \'../img/one.jpg\');\r\n                                                                                     $(\'#three\').attr(\'src\', \'../img/three.jpg\');\r\n                                                                                     $(\'#four\').attr(\'src\', \'../img/four.jpg\');\r\n                                                                                     $(\'#five\').attr(\'src\', \'../img/five.jpg\');\r\n                                                                        });\r\n                                                                          $(\"#three\").click(function ()\r\n					                                 {\r\n										  $(\'#three\').attr(\'src\', \'../images/three_active.jpg\');\r\n                                                                                  $(\'#one\').attr(\'src\', \'../img/one.jpg\');\r\n                                                                                     $(\'#two\').attr(\'src\', \'../img/two.jpg\'); \r\n                                                                                     $(\'#four\').attr(\'src\', \'../img/four.jpg\');\r\n                                                                                     $(\'#five\').attr(\'src\', \'../img/five.jpg\');\r\n                                                                        });\r\n                                                                             $(\"#four\").click(function ()\r\n					                                 {\r\n										    $(\'#four\').attr(\'src\', \'../images/four_active.jpg\');\r\n                                                                                    $(\'#one\').attr(\'src\', \'../img/one.jpg\');\r\n                                                                                     $(\'#two\').attr(\'src\', \'../img/two.jpg\');\r\n                                                                                     $(\'#three\').attr(\'src\', \'../img/three.jpg\');\r\n                                                                                     $(\'#five\').attr(\'src\', \'../img/five.jpg\');\r\n                                                                        });\r\n                                                                               $(\"#five\").click(function ()\r\n					                                 {\r\n										  $(\'#five\').attr(\'src\', \'../images/five_active.jpg\');\r\n                                                                                  $(\'#one\').attr(\'src\', \'../img/one.jpg\');\r\n                                                                                     $(\'#two\').attr(\'src\', \'../img/two.jpg\');\r\n                                                                                     $(\'#three\').attr(\'src\', \'../img/three.jpg\');\r\n                                                                                     $(\'#four\').attr(\'src\', \'../img/four.jpg\');\r\n                                                                                    \r\n                                                                        });\r\n\r\n                                                });\r\n</script>\r\n                        <div class=\"vision\">\r\n              <h2>Strength that makes us special.</h2>\r\n              <div class=\"down\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n              <div class=\"down\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n              <nav>\r\n                <ul id=\"tabs\">\r\n                  <li> <a class=\"current\" href=\"#\"><img src=\"../img/one.jpg\"  id=\"one\" style=\"padding-left: 57px; margin-bottom: 8px;\" /><br />\r\n                    Temple & Prayer hall</a>\r\n                    <p style=\"margin:0px;\">Features</p>\r\n                  </li>\r\n                  <li><a href=\"#\"> <img src=\"../img/two.jpg\" id=\"two\" style=\"padding-left: 50px; margin-bottom: 8px;\" /><br />\r\n                    Natural laboratories </a>\r\n                    <p style=\"margin:0px;\">Features</p>\r\n                  </li>\r\n                  <li><a href=\"#\"> <img src=\"../img/three.jpg\"  id=\"three\" style=\"padding-left: 57px; margin-bottom: 8px;\" /><br />\r\n                    Project Vrindaranyam</a>\r\n                    <p style=\"margin:0px;\">Features</p>\r\n                  </li>\r\n                  <li><a href=\"#\"> <img src=\"../img/four.jpg\" id=\"four\"  style=\"padding-left: 28px; margin-bottom: 8px;\" /><br />\r\n                    Project Prithvi</a>\r\n                    <p style=\"margin:0px;\">Features</p>\r\n                  </li>\r\n                  <li><a href=\"#\"> <img src=\"../img/five.jpg\"  id=\"five\" style=\"padding-left: 27px; margin-bottom: 8px;\" /><br />\r\n                    Project Surabhi</a>\r\n                    <p style=\"margin:0px;\">Features</p>\r\n                  </li>\r\n                </ul>\r\n                <span id=\"indicator\"></span> </nav>\r\n              <div id=\"content\">\r\n                <section>\r\n                  <p>â€¢ Innovations in Food Safety and Food Security<br />\r\n                    â€¢  Studies on Climate, Environment and Ecology<br />\r\n                    â€¢ Environment friendly Technology<br />\r\n                    â€¢ Green Energy<br />\r\n                    â€¢ Preservation of Bio-diversity<br />\r\n                    â€¢ Spiritual Connectivity through Cultural Training using medium of music, dance and performing arts </p>\r\n                </section>\r\n                <section>\r\n                  <p>The most important result of a general character to which the special theory of relativity has led is concerned with the conception of mass. Before the advent of relativity, physics recognised two conservation laws of fundamental importance, namely, the law of the conservation of energy and the law of the conservation of mass these two fundamental laws appeared to be quite independent of each other. By means of the theory of relativity they have been united into one law. We shall now briefly consider how this unification came about, and what meaning is to be attached to it.</p>\r\n                </section>\r\n                <section>\r\n                  <p>â€¢ A conservation center for the depleting forest resources around the Vraja area.<br />\r\n                    â€¢ An important educational park for school students.<br />\r\n                    â€¢ Outdoor education facility for students bridging the growing gap between nature and\r\n                    urbanization.<br />\r\n                    â€¢ A conservatory for rare and indigenous species of Indian trees</p>\r\n                </section>\r\n                <section>\r\n                  <p>â€¢ The use of synthetic fertilizers and pesticides has destroyed soil quality and has\r\n                    created other environmental and health crises.<br />\r\n                    â€¢ Genetically modified food is a great threat to the humanity at large.<br />\r\n                    â€¢ Under project Prithvi, the organic research centre will develop scientific methodologies for organic farming which is least energy demanding and economically sustainable.<br />\r\n                    â€¢ Regular short courses will be held for the village youth of Vraja area to promote organic farming.</p>\r\n                </section>\r\n                <section>\r\n                  <p>Most of the goshalas in our country are run on charity and are not economically viable. Project Surabhi will be demonstrated to be economically viable model which shall then be replicated in few villages of Vraja as a resource of\r\n                    economy and employment generation</p>\r\n                  <p>Project Surabhi will demonstrate the complementary use of cowproducts the form of diary items, medicine and energy while allowing the cows to have enough grazing lands.</p>\r\n                  <p>The science of cow protection will be developed in BGIS.</p>\r\n                </section>\r\n              </div>\r\n                 <div class=\"down\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"down\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n              <h1 style=\"margin-bottom:15px;\"><img src=\"../img/six.jpg\"  style=\"margin-bottom: -15px;margin-right: 8px;\" />Eco Friendly Campus</h1>\r\n              <div id=\"slidorion\">\r\n                <div id=\"slider\">\r\n                  <div class=\"slider-image\" rel=\"section1\"> <img src=\"../img/eco1.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"400\" /> </div>\r\n                  <div class=\"slider-image\" rel=\"section2\"> <img src=\"../img/eco2.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"400\" /> </div>\r\n                  <div class=\"slider-image\" rel=\"section3\"> <img src=\"../img/eco3.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"400\" /> </div>\r\n                  <div class=\"slider-image\" rel=\"section4\"> <img src=\"../img/eco4.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"400\" /> </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div id=\"accordion\">\r\n                  <div class=\"header\"><a class=\"slider-link\" rel=\"section1\">Site Design Starategies</a></div>\r\n                  <div class=\"content\">\r\n                    <p>â€¢ Rain Water Harvesting, ground water recharging <br />\r\n                      â€¢ Water Recycling and Conservation<br />\r\n                      â€¢ Local/ Native plantation encouraged<br />\r\n                      <span style=\"color:#c71111; font-size:12px; padding-left:5px;\">Energy Saving : UPTO 50% </span></p>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                  <div class=\"header\"><a class=\"slider-link\" rel=\"section2\">Building Design Starategies</a></div>\r\n                  <div class=\"content\">\r\n                    <p>â€¢ Day lighting encouraged through singly loaded corridor <br />\r\n                      â€¢ Green/ insulated roofs<br />\r\n                      â€¢ Recessed windows with Jharokas to reduce heat gain.<br />\r\n                      <span style=\"color:#c71111; font-size:12px; padding-left:5px;\">Energy Saving : UPTO 50% </span></p>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                  <div class=\"header\"><a class=\"slider-link\" rel=\"section3\">Sanitary Design Starategies</a></div>\r\n                  <div class=\"content\">\r\n                    <p>â€¢ Use of low flow fixtures <br />\r\n                      â€¢ Recycling of Grey Waters<br />\r\n                      â€¢ Use of Recycled water<br />\r\n                      â€¢ Less load on treatment plant.<br />\r\n                      <span style=\"color:#c71111; font-size:12px; padding-left:5px;\">Energy Saving : UPTO 30% </span></p>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                  <div class=\"header\"><a class=\"slider-link\" rel=\"section4\">Electrical Design Starategies</a></div>\r\n                  <div class=\"content\">\r\n                    <p>â€¢ Use of T-5/ LED Lamps UPTO 40%<br />\r\n                      â€¢ Use of electronic ballasts in fixtures<br />\r\n                      â€¢ Maximized natural lightingUse of Recycled water<br />\r\n                      â€¢ Solar heating.<br />\r\n                      <span style=\"color:#c71111; font-size:12px; padding-left:5px;\">Energy Saving : UPTO 40%</span></p>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n              </div>\r\n                            <div class=\"down\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n                       <div class=\"down\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n              <h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"../img/seven.jpg\"  style=\"margin-bottom: -15px;margin-right: 8px;\" />Spiritual touch to modern education</h1>\r\n              <h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Complete knowledge</h2>\r\n              <div class=\"knowledge\">\r\n                <div class=\"icosnball\"><img src=\"../img/iocns.jpg\" /></div>\r\n                <div class=\"redcolor\">\r\n                  <div class=\"specialions1\"><img src=\"../img/studentratio.jpg\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" />Student teacher ratio 1:10</div>\r\n                  <div class=\"specialions2\"><img src=\"../img/teacherstudent.jpg\" style=\"vertical-align:middle; float:left;\"  />Each Teacher has an impeccable character \r\n                    which naturally inspires students to imbibe\r\n                    the same. </div>\r\n                  <div class=\"specialions1\"><img src=\"../img/publish.jpg\" style=\"vertical-align:middle; float:left;\" />In house publish general \r\n                    outdoor education and exposure</div>\r\n                </div>\r\n              </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n                   <div class=\"videoproject\"><img src=\"../img/videoicons.jpg\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" />This unique Project Vrindaaranyam <br/>\r\n                   <a href =\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rdlfH3lrIUQ\"  target=\"_new\"><img src=\"../img/videowhatmakes.jpg\"  /></a>\r\n                  </div>\r\n<br/>', '2014-05-09', 0);
